sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant R as Retriever
    participant A as Agent
    participant P as Policy
    participant T as Tool

    rect rgb(255,245,245)
    Note over U,T: Before mitigation
    U->>A: Summarize document
    A->>R: Fetch context
    R-->>A: Poisoned instruction text
    A->>T: shell.exec command
    T-->>A: Command output
    end

    rect rgb(245,255,245)
    Note over U,T: After mitigation
    U->>A: Summarize document
    A->>R: Fetch context
    R-->>A: Poisoned text
    A->>P: Request shell.exec
    P-->>A: Deny (intent-tool mismatch)
    A-->>U: Safe fallback response
    end
